content":"### New Email Form Submission\n\nServes an n8n-hosted form (From, Subject, Receivedat). Each submission becomes one execution.\n\nNext: Required Fields Present?","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"53cca7e8-b06c-ec36-7f09-597733c41b45","name":"Note: New Email Form Submission"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Required Fields Present?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.from }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Score the Lead · ②→ Abort — Malformed Input","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"d5cbb195-de7e-df1d-158d-50ba60edf325","name":"Note: Required Fields Present?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Abort — Malformed Input\n\nFails fast with a clear message; triggers the error workflow instead of processing bad data.","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,1030],"id":"17c495e4-8aac-bc8d-39f1-df6c4ba55264","name":"Note: Abort — Malformed Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Score the Lead\n\nCustom JavaScript: Score each email 0-100 from simple heuristics\n\nNext: Assign Round-Robin Owner","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"603a2d5f-d231-3b89-b7fa-50016bda6fb8","name":"Note: Score the Lead"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Assign Round-Robin Owner\n\nCustom JavaScript: Round-robin owner assignment\n\nNext: Route by Heat","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"acea126e-2fb4-a621-e10d-7e3e9ed96bd7","name":"Note: Assign Round-Robin Owner"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Route by Heat\n\nRoutes each item to one of 3 lanes: hot, warm + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Hot → Google Sheets + Instant Ping · ②→ Warm → Drip via Outlook · ③→ Cold → Park in Nurture List","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"01eb5cb8-24b2-eac1-c3fd-032c5510f4b7","name":"Note: Route by Heat"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hot → Google Sheets + Instant Ping\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Notify Assigned Owner · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,40],"id":"cb5b8f93-d104-a84a-031f-6dd4423bfd21","name":"Note: Hot → Google Sheets + Instant Ping"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Notify Assigned Owner\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Combine Lead Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,40],"id":"0d73c66d-ff82-071d-e816-905fc17cb78a","name":"Note: Notify Assigned Owner"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Warm → Drip via Outlook\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Combine Lead Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,520],"id":"af1b4958-7753-4bf0-d74b-3f4910fa7d5e","name":"Note: Warm → Drip via Outlook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cold → Park in Nurture List\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Combine Lead Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,1000],"id":"45aa569e-902b-9956-6356-7b29159d63e7","name":"Note: Cold → Park in Nurture List"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Combine Lead Paths\n\nRejoins 3 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Stamp Completion Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"a62cbe12-8d70-828c-fc99-31a3e311a1b0","name":"Note: Combine Lead Paths"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"3412fa37-dcf7-c04c-43bb-1d32a8164979","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Enrich with Reference Data","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"4a6be948-c68c-e1f2-83b7-ab977322e754","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"422eaad8-2664-4e5a-ece3-4acbab5ccc87","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"c8a34c32-2693-edce-af86-167f37d4e4c5","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"6194625c-e112-3c54-4854-314c209fb610","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Outlook · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,520],"id":"eb26970b-603e-5557-86a6-dbb04e9e45ff","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Outlook\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,520],"id":"86702786-584b-2eff-a190-14be44c97f08","name":"Note: Send Summary to Outlook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,1540],"id":"320e1290-639e-4abf-672e-36850192106c","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,1540],"id":"69a84a57-ed09-a961-3b1d-cb700083c9ff","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,1540],"id":"f9225024-46e5-a361-4018-bcaf816bcc88","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Log form submissions with Google Sheets and Outlook without manual work\n\n**Pattern:** Form Intake · **Level:** Production · **Trigger:** Form\n\n## What it does\nLog form submissions with Google Sheets and Outlook without manual work. It starts from a hosted form submission.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual inbox triage is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nNew Email Form Submission → Required Fields Present? → Score the Lead → Assign Round-Robin Owner → Route by Heat → Hot → Google Sheets + Instant Ping → Notify Assigned Owner → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to form intake without manual effort\n- Anyone automating inbox triage in marketing\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Improves response time\n- Responds in seconds\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2 / service account; Microsoft OAuth2; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"0e43e799-7429-2fc5-a351-5603f389f30b","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-500],"id":"85b2eaf3-6877-39ae-b3f4-525c06e23837","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your inbox triage process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-500],"id":"6534ecd2-fe15-e3d6-670f-5eea6912b875","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"New Email Form Submission":{"main":[[{"node":"Required Fields Present?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Required Fields Present?":{"main":[[{"node":"Score the Lead","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Abort — Malformed Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Score the Lead":{"main":[[{"node":"Assign Round-Robin Owner","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Assign Round-Robin Owner":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Heat","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Hot → Google Sheets + Instant Ping":{"main":[[{"node":"Notify Assigned Owner","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Heat":{"main":[[{"node":"Hot → Google Sheets + Instant Ping","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Warm → Drip via Outlook","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Cold → Park in Nurture List","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Notify Assigned Owner":{"main":[[{"node":"Combine Lead Paths","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Warm → Drip via Outlook":{"main":[[{"node":"Combine Lead Paths","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cold → Park in Nurture List":{"main":[[{"node":"Combine Lead Paths","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Combine Lead Paths":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich with Reference Data","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich with Reference Data":{"main":[[{"node":"Fold In Enrichment Fields","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fold In Enrichment Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Outlook","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Outlook":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"c6b0136f-833d-41f8-be73-a995aa05ef4d","id":"FDX01994"}